# Privacy Policy for QR Scanner App

Last updated: February 1, 2025

## Introduction

Welcome to the QR Scanner App privacy policy. At QR Scanner App, we take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our QR Scanner application.

## Information We Collect

### Camera Access
- We require camera access solely for scanning QR codes
- Camera data is processed in real-time and is not stored or transmitted
- No images or videos are saved from your camera

### App Permissions
- Camera permission: Required for basic app functionality
- No other permissions are required or requested

### Technical Data
We collect minimal technical information necessary for app functionality:
- Device model
- Operating system version
- App performance data
- Crash reports

## How We Use Your Information

### QR Code Scanning
- QR code content is processed locally on your device
- Scanned data is displayed only to you
- No scanned data is stored permanently
- No data is transmitted to our servers

### App Improvement
- Technical data is used solely for:
  - Bug fixing
  - Performance optimization
  - App stability improvements

## Data Storage and Security
- All processing occurs locally on your device
- No personal data is stored on external servers
- No cloud storage is used
- No data sharing with third parties

## Children's Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect information from children under 13. The app is suitable for general audiences but parental guidance is recommended.

## Your Rights
You have the right to:
- Access your data
- Request data deletion
- Opt-out of future updates
- Contact us with privacy concerns

## Updates to Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy periodically. Users will be notified of any significant changes.

## Contact Information
For privacy-related questions or concerns, contact us at:
[Your Contact Information]

## Compliance
This app complies with:
- Google Play Store policies
- GDPR requirements
- CCPA requirements
- COPPA guidelines

## Data Protection Measures
- Local-only processing
- No network data transmission
- Secure data handling
- Regular security updates

## Third-Party Services
This app does not use any third-party services that collect user data.

## Data Retention
- No permanent storage of scanned QR codes
- Technical data retained only for the duration necessary for app functionality
- Crash reports automatically deleted after issue resolution

## User Control
You can:
- Clear app data through Android settings
- Revoke camera permissions at any time
- Uninstall the app to remove all local data

## Security Practices
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your privacy:
- Local data processing
- No external server communication
- Regular security audits
- Prompt vulnerability fixes

## Acceptance of Policy
By using our app, you acknowledge this privacy policy and consent to its terms.
